1. Product definition

One-line description

Nightingale is an ambient, nurse-governed clinical co-pilot that converts bedside care into verified documentation, shift memory, risk signals, and operational assistance.

Core users

Primary:
	•	bedside RNs
	•	charge nurses

Secondary:
	•	LPNs
	•	CNAs/techs
	•	case managers
	•	hospitalists
	•	quality/compliance teams
	•	nurse managers

Core promise

Less charting. More nursing. Better memory. Fewer misses.

