12. MVP

The right MVP is not “fully ambient AI nurse brain.”

It is a narrow, painful wedge with fast proof.

MVP scope

Medical-surgical floor, day shift, one EHR, one hospital.

MVP capabilities
	•	voice-to-note
	•	shift summary drafting
	•	handoff generation
	•	pain med follow-up detection
	•	chart gap detection
	•	carry-forward with change-only confirmation
	•	suggestion queue

Explicitly not in MVP
	•	autonomous ambient room listening by default
	•	complex diagnosis models
	•	full unit staffing optimization
	•	cross-specialty expansion
	•	provider order suggestions

Why this wedge

It creates immediate value while avoiding the highest-trust-risk surfaces.

